name: Vessels 195: Randall
description:
Randall, one of the arena's most despised pilots, cheated his way to the top of the ranks. Sabotage is his favourite method of victory. Countless mechs mysteriously malfunctioned during battle. One day Randall's misdeeds lead to a great tragedy. A cut fuel line and a few sparks ended the life of a young pilot in a blaze of sadness...

The saboteur reveled in the victory as cries of pain and sadness rang out from the crowd. From that day forward Randall embraced the infamy and sunk further into the depths of villainy.
